[0m[49m[38;5;10m+      3[0m:[38;5;10m[49m **Reviewer:** Technical Expert Panel (Security, Architecture, Networking, Voice)
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+      4[0m:[38;5;10m[49m **Document:** `chapter07.10-optimal-intervention-timing-prediction.md`
